## 5. Icon System

- **Code:** Lucide PascalCase names (`Heart`, `ChevronDown`) â€” see `frontend/src/components/Icon.js`
- **Figma:** Lucide Icons library (subscribed); swap via INSTANCE_SWAP, never variant-per-icon

## 6. Styling Approach

- Global foundation stylesheet ships from WP and is injected/mirrored on the frontend
- Fluid type via `clamp()`; spacing in rem
- Control height: `--kpf-control-height` (2.75rem); radius pill for buttons
- Prefer semantic tokens in new work: `color/bg/*`, `color/text/*`, `color/border/*`, `color/action/*`

