## Agent rules when editing Figma

1. Load `figma-use` + `figma-generate-library` before `use_figma`
2. Bind fills/strokes/gaps/radii to variables â€” no raw hex in components
3. Label docs: **blue** = semantic token, **green** = CSS class / primitive name
4. One `setCurrentPageAsync` per `use_figma` call; never parallelize mutating `use_figma`
5. Return all created node/variable IDs; tag with `dsb` sharedPluginData
